{"id": 19, "ts": 1778865581.1030304, "event": "public_discussion_message", "round": 2, "agent": "agent_3", "message": "Based on the attributes we each have, I see the following trade\u2011offs:\n* **Reliability & calmness** \u2013 Candidate\u202fB is the only one explicitly described as \u201c100\u202f% reliable\u201d and \u201ckeeps calm in a crisis.\u201d Those are strong points for long\u2011distance operations.\n* **Technical / cognitive competence** \u2013 Candidates\u202fA, D and C all show strong technical abilities (anticipating danger, problem\u2011solving, quick correct decisions).\n* **Decision\u2011making under pressure** \u2013 Candidate\u202fC \u201ccan make correct decisions quickly,\u201d which is a clear advantage for high\u2011stress situations.\n* **Teamwork / crew cooperation** \u2013 Candidate\u202fC \u201cputs concern for others above everything,\u201d indicating a crew\u2011focused attitude. Candidate\u202fB is noted as \u201cpretentious\u201d and \u201csometimes adopts the wrong tone when communicating,\u201d and Candidate\u202fD is described as a \u201cloner\u201d and \u201cmoody,\u201d while Candidate\u202fA is \u201cunfriendly.\u201d These interpersonal weaknesses could jeopardise crew coordination on long\u2011haul flights.\n* **Professional development** \u2013 Candidate\u202fC is \u201cnot very willing to further his education,\u201d and Candidate\u202fB\u2019s \u201cexcellent computer skills\u201d are useful but not decisive.\nWhen weighing the most safety\u2011critical factors\u2014reliability, calmness, sound judgment, and especially crew cooperation\u2014I find Candidate\u202fC\u2019s combination of rapid, correct decision\u2011making and a clear concern for others outweighs his communication difficulty and limited desire for further education. Candidate\u202fB\u2019s reliability and calmness are excellent, but his pretentiousness and tone issues pose a higher risk to crew dynamics than the drawbacks seen in C.\n**Therefore, I support Candidate\u202fC as the best overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
